{"tid":1080775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【救救地球】英沙灘埋住80年代包裝垃圾 部份當「古董」送入博物館","createTime":"2019-03-27T23:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T00:33:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b51e919057149b60d9eed22a31429e5a10974fa","tid":1080775,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:44:03.000Z","msg":"英國一班清潔沙灘的義工找到80年代的「古董」零食包裝袋及汽水罐等垃圾，當中有不少品牌已經消失逾10年，令人大感驚奇。活動負責人表示此證明塑膠垃圾難以分解，好處是部份「古董」可送去博物館。<br />\n康沃爾郡紐基市（Newquay）義工組織「Fistral Beach Clean」在一次清潔沙灘活動中，發現了一堆「古董」垃圾，包括舊時常見但現已停產的零食品牌包裝袋，如薄荷朱古力餅「Mint Cracknel」、朱古力品牌「Snickers」前身「Marathon」、健怡橙汁汽水「One Cal」、香蕉味汽水「Corona Banana soda」等。<br />\n估計這堆垃圾已被埋在沙丘下30年，直至早前一次風暴令沙丘倒塌才曝光。有可口可樂罐上印有的「銷售日期」為1984年，一包鹽和醋味薯片包裝上印有「最佳食用日期」為1984年，而且還附送當年時興的《奪寶奇兵之魔域奇兵》（Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom）海報。<br />\n「Fistral Beach Clean」負責人古多爾（Andy Goodal）表示︰「事實證明了沙堆裏的垃圾不會被分解，會一直被埋藏至很多代以後。」他已將部份垃圾送往紐基市博物館，對方亦表示很有興趣收藏，而且部份包裝袋是保存狀況良好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190327/large/1553674978_0d61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190327%2Flarge%2F1553674978_0d61.jpg&h=15b20fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190327/large/1553674978_3b90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190327%2Flarge%2F1553674978_3b90.jpg&h=925dd6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190328/59417417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190328%2F59417417&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlzr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=f164ec8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190328%2F59417417&h=a9098ad0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190328/59417417</a>"},{"pid":"5b747ba62438ef8eda6d03001703214f34afa080","tid":1080775,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾博物館幾特別"},{"pid":"97b07af54f7385b43808f114b29e9465d728e56c","tid":1080775,"uid":71624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b747ba62438ef8eda6d03001703214f34afa080","tid":1080775,"uid":175077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾博物館幾特別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"就好似有d名畫唔講你知，可能你都會以為係細路仔亂畫"}]}